name: hadoop-cos v8.1.1
body:
Dependence: cos java sdk 5.6.69

Features:

- Get user from ugi
- Set temporary directory to  777
- Fix the scm properties in pom
- flush wait for finish part uploads
- read task retry for all io exception
- support multi compile way to support tencent cloud l5 support from the l5 branch
- fix the preconditions of create method

name: hadoop-cos v8.1.0
body:
Dependence: cos java sdk 5.6.69

Features:

- Fix the L5 support build
- Support cosn://bucket-appid/ to query posix bucket
- Support the extended posix capabilities
- Add the enabled option for the upload part checksum
- Fix the boundedIOThreadPool
- Add the 503 mpu retry
- Support get cos client from nativestore
- From this version not support the hadoop version 2.6.*, because of these version not support the truncate

name: hadoop-cos v5.8.4
body:
# [](https://github.com/tencentyun/hadoop-cos/compare/v5.8.3...v5.8.4) (2020-09-01)


### Bug Fixes

* 修正同时打开多个文件时，缓冲区被耗尽导致的死锁问题 ([a5f1b1b](https://github.com/tencentyun/hadoop-cos/commit/a5f1b1b57537263d21e881b5cf7352c1b6aa3164))
* 修正磁盘缓冲区的默认值为不限制 ([ba43083](https://github.com/tencentyun/hadoop-cos/commit/ba43083d0ef04443c08093e1afed160c429d404b))


### Features

* 修改NativeFileSystemStore接口的访问级别，以支持flink文件系统的特殊语义实现 ([2a7f63a](https://github.com/tencentyun/hadoop-cos/commit/2a7f63ae2a1719c9c0aa8e102df1cf922e1ae6cf))

### Build

* 将原有hadoop-cos-xxx-shaded.jar拆分为hadoop-cos-{hadoop.version}-{version}.jar 和 cos_api-bundle-{version}.jar 两个依赖包，以贴近Hadoop社区的依赖规范。同时，减小引用hadoop-cos依赖包时的冗余依赖 ([93d732e](https://github.com/tencentyun/hadoop-cos/commit/93d7326ecf89308ff98e5750a15c5d98f402cd3d))

* 在包名中引入hadoop-cos的hadoop的版本号与hadoop-cos的版本号机制，方便用户区分具体依赖版本  ([93d732e](https://github.com/tencentyun/hadoop-cos/commit/93d7326ecf89308ff98e5750a15c5d98f402cd3d))

* 考虑到hadoop社区在3.3.0的版本中官方集成了hadoop-cos，大量用户可能还在使用3.3.0以前的hadoop版本，因此，将此版本以前的hadoop-cos的groupId修改到com.qcloud.cos中，同时发布到maven中央仓库，便于开发者在pom中直接引用 ([93d732e](https://github.com/tencentyun/hadoop-cos/commit/93d7326ecf89308ff98e5750a15c5d98f402cd3d))
